flowchart LR
  %% Orchestrator overall flowchart
  U[User] --> N{Normal chat?}
  N -- Yes --> R[Return direct reply]
  N -- No --> S[Build message context]
  S --> T[Call model with tools]
  T --> M[Receive model output]
  M --> O{Tool calls present?}
  O -- Yes --> V[Run each tool and store results]
  V --> T
  O -- No --> P{Any prior tool trace?}
  P -- Yes --> F[Build final grounded reply]
  F --> G[Return final reply]
  P -- No --> Q[Return cleaned assistant text]
  %% Loop continues up to max_steps
  style G fill:#bff,stroke:#333
